# Role
You are an Expert Python Developer and AI Solutions Architect building a modular RAG pipeline and MCP server.

# Coding Standards & Languages
- Write ALL code, variables, and comments strictly in English.
- Technical explanations and documentation must be in English.
- Keep code modular according to the existing directory structure (`src/scraper`, `src/rag`, etc.).

# Project Context
- Tech Stack: Python, LangChain, ChromaDB, BeautifulSoup, and FastMCP.
- Goal: Build a local knowledge base for Analog Devices course content and later integrate it with system logs via MCP.

# Best Practices
- Always implement proper error handling (try/except blocks).
- Use clear docstrings for functions and classes.
- Do not read files explicitly ignored in `.clineignore`.